{"surah":86,"verses":[{"n":1,"key":"86:1","arabic":" وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"By the sky and the night comer","id":"Demi langit dan yang datang pada malam hari.","words":[{"a":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ","en":"By the sky","id":"dan langit"},{"a":"وَٱلطَّارِقِ","en":"and the night comer","id":"dan yang datang di malam hari"}]},{"n":2,"key":"86:2","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"And what can make you know what is the night comer?","id":"Dan tahukah kamu apakah yang datang pada malam hari itu?","words":[{"a":"وَمَآ","en":"And what","id":"dan apa"},{"a":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","en":"can make you know","id":"kamu tahu"},{"a":"مَا","en":"what","id":"apa"},{"a":"ٱلطَّارِقُ","en":"the night comer (is)","id":"yang datang dimalam hari"}]},{"n":3,"key":"86:3","arabic":"ٱلنَّجْمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"It is the piercing star","id":"(Yaitu) bintang yang bersinar tajam,","words":[{"a":"ٱلنَّجْمُ","en":"(It is) the star","id":"bintang"},{"a":"ٱلثَّاقِبُ","en":"the piercing","id":"cemerlang/menembus"}]},{"n":4,"key":"86:4","arabic":"إِن كُلُّ نَفْسٍ لَّمَّا عَلَيْهَا حَافِظٌ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"There is no soul but that it has over it a protector.","id":"setiap orang pasti ada penjaganya.","words":[{"a":"إِن","en":"Not","id":"tidak"},{"a":"كُلُّ","en":"(is) every","id":"setiap"},{"a":"نَفْسٍۢ","en":"soul","id":"jiwa/diri"},{"a":"لَّمَّا","en":"but","id":"melainkan"},{"a":"عَلَيْهَا","en":"over it","id":"atasnya"},{"a":"حَافِظٌۭ","en":"(is) a protector","id":"penjaga"}]},{"n":5,"key":"86:5","arabic":"فَلْيَنظُرِ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"So let man observe from what he was created.","id":"Maka hendaklah manusia memperhatikan dari apa dia diciptakan.","words":[{"a":"فَلْيَنظُرِ","en":"So let see","id":"maka hendaklah memperhatikan"},{"a":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ","en":"man","id":"manusia"},{"a":"مِمَّ","en":"from what","id":"dari apa"},{"a":"خُلِقَ","en":"he is created","id":"ia diciptakan"}]},{"n":6,"key":"86:6","arabic":"خُلِقَ مِن مَّآءٍ دَافِقٍ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"He was created from a fluid, ejected,","id":"Dia diciptakan dari air (mani) yang terpancar,","words":[{"a":"خُلِقَ","en":"He is created","id":"ia diciptakan"},{"a":"مِن","en":"from","id":"dari"},{"a":"مَّآءٍۢ","en":"a water","id":"air"},{"a":"دَافِقٍۢ","en":"ejected","id":"terpancar"}]},{"n":7,"key":"86:7","arabic":"يَخْرُجُ مِنۢ بَيْنِ ٱلصُّلْبِ وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"Emerging from between the backbone and the ribs.","id":"yang keluar dari antara tulang punggung (sulbi) dan tulang dada.","words":[{"a":"يَخْرُجُ","en":"Coming forth","id":"ia keluar"},{"a":"مِنۢ","en":"from","id":"dari"},{"a":"بَيْنِ","en":"between","id":"antara"},{"a":"ٱلصُّلْبِ","en":"the backbone","id":"tulang belakang"},{"a":"وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ","en":"and the ribs","id":"dan tulang dada"}]},{"n":8,"key":"86:8","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجْعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٌ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"Indeed, He [i.e., Allāh], to return him [to life], is Able.","id":"Sungguh, Allah benar-benar kuasa untuk mengembalikannya (hidup setelah mati).","words":[{"a":"إِنَّهُۥ","en":"Indeed, He","id":"sesungguhnya Dia"},{"a":"عَلَىٰ","en":"to","id":"atas"},{"a":"رَجْعِهِۦ","en":"return him","id":"mengembalikanya"},{"a":"لَقَادِرٌۭ","en":"(is) Able","id":"benar-benar berkuasa"}]},{"n":9,"key":"86:9","arabic":"يَوْمَ تُبْلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"The Day when secrets will be put on trial,","id":"Pada hari ditampakkan segala rahasia,","words":[{"a":"يَوْمَ","en":"(The) Day","id":"hari"},{"a":"تُبْلَى","en":"will be tested","id":"dibuka/dinampakkan"},{"a":"ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ","en":"the secrets","id":"rahasia-rahasia"}]},{"n":10,"key":"86:10","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٍ وَلَا نَاصِرٍ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"Then he [i.e., man] will have no power or any helper.","id":"maka manusia tidak lagi mempunyai suatu kekuatan dan tidak (pula) ada penolong.","words":[{"a":"فَمَا","en":"Then not","id":"maka tidak"},{"a":"لَهُۥ","en":"(is) for him","id":"baginya"},{"a":"مِن","en":"any","id":"dari"},{"a":"قُوَّةٍۢ","en":"power","id":"kekuatan"},{"a":"وَلَا","en":"and not","id":"dan tidak"},{"a":"نَاصِرٍۢ","en":"any helper","id":"seorang penolong"}]},{"n":11,"key":"86:11","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجْعِ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"By the sky which sends back","id":"Demi langit yang mengandung hujan,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ","en":"By the sky","id":"dan langit"},{"a":"ذَاتِ","en":"which","id":"mempunyai/mengandung"},{"a":"ٱلرَّجْعِ","en":"returns","id":"air/hujan"}]},{"n":12,"key":"86:12","arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدْعِ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"And [by] the earth which splits,","id":"dan bumi yang mempunyai tumbuh-tumbuhan,","words":[{"a":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","en":"And the earth","id":"dan bumi"},{"a":"ذَاتِ","en":"which","id":"mempunyai"},{"a":"ٱلصَّدْعِ","en":"cracks open","id":"tumbuh-tumbuhan"}]},{"n":13,"key":"86:13","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوْلٌ فَصْلٌ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"Indeed, it [i.e., the Qur’ān] is a decisive statement,","id":"sungguh, (Alquran) itu benar-benar firman pemisah (antara yang hak dan yang batil),","words":[{"a":"إِنَّهُۥ","en":"Indeed, it","id":"sesungguhnya ia (Al Qur'an)"},{"a":"لَقَوْلٌۭ","en":"(is) surely a Word","id":"perkataan/firman"},{"a":"فَصْلٌۭ","en":"decisive","id":"terpisah"}]},{"n":14,"key":"86:14","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلْهَزْلِ","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"And it is not amusement.","id":"dan (Alquran) itu bukanlah senda gurauan.","words":[{"a":"وَمَا","en":"And not","id":"dan tidak"},{"a":"هُوَ","en":"it","id":"ia (Al Qur'an)"},{"a":"بِٱلْهَزْلِ","en":"(is) for amusement","id":"dengan sia-sia/senda gurau"}]},{"n":15,"key":"86:15","arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ يَكِيدُونَ كَيْدًا","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"Indeed, they are planning a plan,","id":"Sungguh, mereka (orang kafir) merencanakan tipu daya yang jahat,","words":[{"a":"إِنَّهُمْ","en":"Indeed, they","id":"sesungguhnya mereka"},{"a":"يَكِيدُونَ","en":"are plotting","id":"mereka membuat tipu daya"},{"a":"كَيْدًۭا","en":"a plot","id":"tipu daya"}]},{"n":16,"key":"86:16","arabic":"وَأَكِيدُ كَيْدًا","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"But I am planning a plan.","id":"dan Aku pun membuat rencana (tipu daya) yang jitu.","words":[{"a":"وَأَكِيدُ","en":"But I am planning","id":"dan AKu membuat tipu daya"},{"a":"كَيْدًۭا","en":"a plan","id":"tipu daya"}]},{"n":17,"key":"86:17","arabic":"فَمَهِّلِ ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ أَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْدًۢا","page":591,"juz":30,"en":"So allow time for the disbelievers. Leave them awhile.","id":"Karena itu berilah penangguhan kepada orang-orang kafir. Berilah mereka kesempatan untuk sementara waktu.","words":[{"a":"فَمَهِّلِ","en":"So give respite","id":"maka beri tangguhlah"},{"a":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","en":"(to) the disbelievers","id":"orang-orang kafir"},{"a":"أَمْهِلْهُمْ","en":"Give respite to them ","id":"beritangguhlah mereka"},{"a":"رُوَيْدًۢا","en":"little","id":"sedikit/sebentar"}]}]}